Ways to get user input 

1) radio buttons 
2) select tag
3) textarea tag


<input type="radio">
only one choice like choosing gender
<input type="checkbox">
allows users to select and unselect

action- the URL to send form data to
method- the type of HTTP request

<input is what goes inside a form

